ADCASTPRODUCT.4OVERALL%2CITPROVIDESA%22%2C%22x%22%3A1110%2C%22y%22%3A746%2C%22width%22%3A211%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DOCUMENTEXPLORESTHEFACTORSTHATHAVE%22%2C%22x%22%3A1109%2C%22y%22%3A567%2C%22width%22%3A192%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ITSADAPTABILITY%2CINCLUSIVITYANDDYNAMIC%22%2C%22x%22%3A1108%2C%22y%22%3A599%2C%22width%22%3A195%2C%22height%22%3A14%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22WHATCHALLENGESHASFOOTGOLFFACEDDESPITE%22%2C%22x%22%3A1110%2C%22y%22%3A905%2C%22width%22%3A205%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22WHATFACTORSCONTRIBUTETOTHESUCCESSOF%22%2C%22x%22%3A1104%2C%22y%22%3A854%2C%22width%22%3A202%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22COMPREHENSIVEPERSPECTIVEONTHERISEOF%22%2C%22x%22%3A1110%2C%22y%22%3A761%2C%22width%22%3A199%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22EXPLORATIONOFAGLOBALSPORTINGPHENOMENON%22%2C%22x%22%3A1114%2C%22y%22%3A483%2C%22width%22%3A205%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22MENTALHEALTHBENEFITSASSOCIATEDWITHTHESPORT.%22%2C%22x%22%3A1111%2C%22y%22%3A680%2C%22width%22%3A228%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22PICKLEBALLASAGLOBALSPORTINGSENSATION.S%22%2C%22x%22%3A1108%2C%22y%22%3A776%2C%22width%22%3A199%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ALASSISTANTBETA%22%2C%22x%22%3A520%2C%22y%22%3A62%2C%22width%22%3A167%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22RECREATIONALSPORT.TFROMITSORIGINSASA%22%2C%22x%22%3A1109%2C%22y%22%3A536%2C%22width%22%3A195%2C%22height%22%3A14%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22INTRIGUINGPREMISE%3F%22%2C%22x%22%3A510%2C%22y%22%3A1072%2C%22width%22%3A178%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%222THEDOCUMENTALSODISCUSSESTHEROLEOFSOCIAL%22%2C%22x%22%3A1111%2C%22y%22%3A695%2C%22width%22%3A230%2C%22height%22%3A16%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22TIOPY%22%2C%22x%22%3A1108%2C%22y%22%3A806%2C%22width%22%3A198%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22GAMEPLAY.2ITEXAMINESTHESTRATEGICAND%22%2C%22x%22%3A1108%2C%22y%22%3A616%2C%22width%22%3A204%2C%22height%22%3A12%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%89%22%2C%22x%22%3A13%2C%22y%22%3A409%2C%22width%22%3A35%2C%22height%22%3A170%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22CHECKRESPONSESANDSOURCES.LEARNMORE%22%2C%22x%22%3A474%2C%22y%22%3A1325%2C%22width%22%3A257%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ICOPY%22%2C%22x%22%3A498%2C%22y%22%3A851%2C%22width%22%3A79%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22SPIKEBALL%3F%22%2C%22x%22%3A515%2C%22y%22%3A975%2C%22width%22%3A92%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22INTRIGUINGPREMISE%3F%22%2C%22x%22%3A1112%2C%22y%22%3A921%2C%22width%22%3A127%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22WEBSITE%22%2C%22x%22%3A498%2C%22y%22%3A156%2C%22width%22%3A72%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22THERISEOFPICKLEBALL%3AACOMPREHENSIVE%22%2C%22x%22%3A1113%2C%22y%22%3A469%2C%22width%22%3A187%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22SPIKEBALL%3F%22%2C%22x%22%3A1103%2C%22y%22%3A869%2C%22width%22%3A188%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22Q%E6%88%B7%22%2C%22x%22%3A803%2C%22y%22%3A853%2C%22width%22%3A108%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22CONTRIBUTEDTOPICKLEBALL'SPOPULARITY%2CINCLUD%22%2C%22x%22%3A1110%2C%22y%22%3A585%2C%22width%22%3A201%2C%22height%22%3A16%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22G%22%2C%22x%22%3A474%2C%22y%22%3A1251%2C%22width%22%3A41%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22WEBSITE%22%2C%22x%22%3A1111%2C%22y%22%3A434%2C%22width%22%3A121%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22.CLOADINABESURETODOUBLE%22%2C%22x%22%3A667%2C%22y%22%3A1294%2C%22width%22%3A249%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%239e9e9e%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ue15fff50%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u89969fd9\" id=\"u89969fd9\" style=\"text-align: center\"><em><span data-lake-id=\"u3c0e5e85\" id=\"u3c0e5e85\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">在AI助手中提示文档的抽象。</span></em></p><p data-lake-id=\"u9e8fd143\" id=\"u9e8fd143\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8ba54d8f\" id=\"u8ba54d8f\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">作为内部测试流程的一部分，研究人员还成立了一个由近 80 名员工组成的员工顾问委员会，代表了不同的角色，包括财务、法律、人力资源、营销、战略、研究和销售。由于每项工作都有一组独特的用例、需求和行为，这些用例、需求和行为会影响他们如何使用测试版，</span><span data-lake-id=\"u0a8504d8\" id=\"u0a8504d8\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36); background-color: #FBDE28\">因此特定的工作职能帮助我们发现了尝试使用这些功能来满足特定需求的人们可能会出现的可用性问题。</span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"oHVI8\" id=\"oHVI8\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua3b845d0\" id=\"ua3b845d0\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">通过构建框架来定义质量</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u7d54bed8\" id=\"u7d54bed8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6899745c\" id=\"u6899745c\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">通过 Adobe Design Research &amp; Strategy，我们开始通过全面评估人们如何看待他们的整体体验、功能如何满足他们的需求以及功能如何与他们的期望保持一致来衡量功能的质量。我们还向 Adobe Firefly 团队学习，了解他们如何衡量质量并密切关注市场格局，以便我们能够更好地了解生成式 AI 满足的需求，并了解哪些工具对人们最有价值。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u1ee032b6\" id=\"u1ee032b6\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8076e763\" id=\"u8076e763\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">这些信息和定性研究形成了一个质量框架，使我们能够诚实地判断我们是否满足了人们的需求。它基于三个参数：</span></p><ul list=\"u4fa26db2\"><li fid=\"ubb82ec0f\" data-lake-id=\"uf99115bc\" id=\"uf99115bc\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u18cd9319\" id=\"u18cd9319\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">有用吗？</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uaac16a06\" id=\"uaac16a06\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">这些功能在帮助人们实现目标方面是否有效且有价值？</span></li><li fid=\"ubb82ec0f\" data-lake-id=\"u33250880\" id=\"u33250880\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uca89e09a\" id=\"uca89e09a\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">可以用吗？</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4d92feb0\" id=\"u4d92feb0\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">界面是否易于理解和使用，功能是否有助于理解和参与？</span></li><li fid=\"ubb82ec0f\" data-lake-id=\"udaf6dcb5\" id=\"udaf6dcb5\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue8642e86\" id=\"ue8642e86\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">有责任吗？</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6d88a654\" id=\"u6d88a654\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">人们是否受到保护，免受刻板印象、偏见、亵渎、暴力或性内容以及有害引用的影响？他们可以信任这些功能吗？这些功能的限制和功能是否清楚？人们报告反馈是否容易？</span></li></ul><h1 data-lake-id=\"lGGmA\" id=\"lGGmA\"><span data-lake-id=\"ueeb2f5c8\" id=\"ueeb2f5c8\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">使用质量框架来推动决策并满足用户需求</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"ub54185e5\" id=\"ub54185e5\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6e7948a9\" id=\"u6e7948a9\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">根据研究和景观分析，当试图在我们目标的质量维度上协调跨职能团队时，该框架非常有帮助。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ue6947c39\" id=\"ue6947c39\"><span data-lake-id=\"u91345742\" id=\"u91345742\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">Adobe Design Research &amp; Strategy 使用它来基准测试和衡量访谈和调查中的体验质量。我们的设计师用它来通过内部测试（通过实际使用来测试功能）和端到端审核来评估体验，作为一个框架来优先考虑工程团队发现的设计错误，并作为一个景观分析的框架，这样我们就可以更好地了解 Acrobat 与其他产品相比如何。所有这些活动最终促成了星级评定，用于告知我们的发布准备情况。它还创建了一系列简化决策的启发式方法，因为它使每个人都可以轻松理解并协调我们想要进行体验改进背后的原因。我们可以简单地说“需要 XYZ 功能来提高可用性”，它将有助于推动功能的积压和路线图。这如何改变部分体验的示例：</span></p><ul list=\"ua90f1043\"><li fid=\"u56ccc0f7\" data-lake-id=\"u6de12131\" id=\"u6de12131\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u254bb290\" id=\"u254bb290\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">前期概述：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u10ec5652\" id=\"u10ec5652\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">最初，一旦处理完文档，AI 助手就会提供建议的问题。但我们从研究中了解到，人们需要一些东西来引导自己阅读文档，以帮助理解所建议的问题。立即提供简短的摘要（文档概述）有助于提供该背景信息。</span></li><li fid=\"u56ccc0f7\" data-lake-id=\"u10f23114\" id=\"u10f23114\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ud734ebb4\" id=\"ud734ebb4\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">建议的问题结构：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub907b0a1\" id=\"ub907b0a1\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">最初建议的问题对于文档来说非常具体，这是一件好事，但复合问题也很复杂。第一次加载文档时，感觉很不舒服。我们与即时工程人员合作，重组和简化了最初建议的问题，并对打开文档时似乎更常见的问题进行了硬编码，例如“提供前五个关键要点”。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u78611c89\" id=\"u78611c89\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1712049910232-728fbc08-78f0-49ea-977c-4256de68e112.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u34ea9cf8-65b9-41f7-b715-2518547027a%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u87ec4251-bfe4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A492323%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1400%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22AL-GENERATEDRESPONSESMAYBEINACCURATEORMISLEADING.BESURET%22%2C%22x%22%3A477%2C%22y%22%3A1304%2C%22width%22%3A383%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22WHATLEDTOPICKLEBALL'SGROWTHFROMABACKYARD%22%2C%22x%22%3A496%2C%22y%22%3A993%2C%22width%22%3A410%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22WHATLEDTOPICKLEBALL'SGROWTHFROMABACKYARD%22%2C%22x%22%3A1104%2C%22y%22%3A881%2C%22width%22%3A226%2C%22height%22%3A16%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ELEMENTS%2CASWELLASCOMPARINGITTOTENNISAND%22%2C%22x%22%3A495%2C%22y%22%3A817%2C%22width%22%3A404%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ECREATIONALSPORT%2CEXPLORINGITSHISTORICAL%22%2C%22x%22%3A500%2C%22y%22%3A756%2C%22width%22%3A386%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22EVOLUTION%2CCURRENTPOPULARITYTRENDS%2CANDSTRATEGIC%22%2C%22x%22%3A496%2C%22y%22%3A788%2C%22width%22%3A417%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22THEDOCUMENTISABOUTTHERISEOFPICKLEBALLASA%22%2C%22x%22%3A498%2C%22y%22%3A726%2C%22width%22%3A401%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ASKAQUESTIONABOUTTHISDOCUMENT%22%2C%22x%22%3A488%2C%22y%22%3A1172%2C%22width%22%3A290%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22CHECKRESPONSESANDSOURCES.LEARNMORE%22%2C%22x%22%3A479%2C%22y%22%3A1325%2C%22width%22%3A247%2C%22height%22%3A16%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22HEDOCUMENTISABOUTTHERISEOFPICKLEBALLAS%22%2C%22x%22%3A1118%2C%22y%22%3A739%2C%22width%22%3A201%2C%22height%22%3A14%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ECREATIONALSPORT%2CEXPLORINGITSHISTORICAL%22%2C%22x%22%3A1117%2C%22y%22%3A757%2C%22width%22%3A202%2C%22height%22%3A10%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22EVOLUTION%2CCURRENTPOPULARITYTRENDS%2CANDSTRATEGI%22%2C%22x%22%3A1114%2C%22y%22%3A774%2C%22width%22%3A216%2C%22height%22%3A10%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22GENERATINGRESPONSE..%22%2C%22x%22%3A562%2C%22y%22%3A1089%2C%22width%22%3A185%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ELEMENTS%2CASWELLASCOMPARINGITTOTENNISAND%22%2C%22x%22%3A1114%2C%22y%22%3A789%2C%22width%22%3A212%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ALASSISTANTBETA%22%2C%22x%22%3A529%2C%22y%22%3A61%2C%22width%22%3A153%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22GENERATINGRESPONS%22%2C%22x%22%3A1098%2C%22y%22%3A931%2C%22width%22%3A144%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22TABLETENNIS.%22%2C%22x%22%3A495%2C%22y%22%3A849%2C%22width%22%3A172%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ASKAQUESTIONABOUTTHISDOCUM%22%2C%22x%22%3A1069%2C%22y%22%3A975%2C%22width%22%3A182%2C%22height%22%3A14%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ICOPY%22%2C%22x%22%3A500%2C%22y%22%3A902%2C%22width%22%3A79%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22OVERVIEW%22%2C%22x%22%3A497%2C%22y%22%3A695%2C%22width%22%3A87%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22TABLETENNIS.%22%2C%22x%22%3A1111%2C%22y%22%3A804%2C%22width%22%3A96%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22STOP%22%2C%22x%22%3A820%2C%22y%22%3A1088%2C%22width%22%3A41%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22P%E5%A6%82%22%2C%22x%22%3A817%2C%22y%22%3A902%2C%22width%22%3A92%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22TCOPY%22%2C%22x%22%3A1112%2C%22y%22%3A834%2C%22width%22%3A51%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%AD%E6%88%B7%22%2C%22x%22%3A1250%2C%22y%22%3A832%2C%22width%22%3A91%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22000%22%2C%22x%22%3A493%2C%22y%22%3A1087%2C%22width%22%3A62%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22GAME%3F%22%2C%22x%22%3A1104%2C%22y%22%3A896%2C%22width%22%3A191%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22GAME%22%2C%22x%22%3A495%2C%22y%22%3A1026%2C%22width%22%3A115%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22VERVIEW%22%2C%22x%22%3A1117%2C%22y%22%3A721%2C%22width%22%3A90%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22G%22%2C%22x%22%3A482%2C%22y%22%3A1248%2C%22width%22%3A35%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22.NPOCRETODOUBLE%22%2C%22x%22%3A658%2C%22y%22%3A1286%2C%22width%22%3A260%2C%22height%22%3A33%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22SSISTANTEENM%22%2C%22x%22%3A1149%2C%22y%22%3A384%2C%22width%22%3A74%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22CHEKP8%E6%9C%89A%E5%8F%B7OU%E5%8A%A1%3ALCANM%E7%94%9F%22%2C%22x%22%3A974%2C%22y%22%3A1052%2C%22width%22%3A303%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23a5a5a5%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u03af76a5%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u928c2627\" id=\"u928c2627\" style=\"text-align: center\"><em><span data-lake-id=\"u03c39513\" id=\"u03c39513\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">AI Assistant 中的前期概述。</span></em></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"cbAeq\" id=\"cbAeq\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5e2d28b8\" id=\"u5e2d28b8\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">Acrobat 和 Acrobat Reader 中生成式 AI 的未来之路</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u48a8e560\" id=\"u48a8e560\"><span data-lake-id=\"u636a3456\" id=\"u636a3456\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">此次公开测试版是 Acrobat 首次尝试使用生成式 AI 来履行 Adobe 对知识民主化的承诺。由于设计团队始终专注于设计优质体验，我们的内部客户提供了他们对这些功能应如何工作的见解、偏好和需求。我们前面有一个深入而丰富的功能路线图，但随着我们的发展，我们将继续专注于使体验成为一种高质量的体验。</span><a href=\"https://helpx.adobe.com/acrobat/using/generative-ai.html\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"uafb1aab9\" id=\"uafb1aab9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u626b83a4\" id=\"u626b83a4\">尝试 Acrobat 中的新生成式 AI 功能。</span></a></p>"}
